{"tid":1652390,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 比利時兼歐洲議會議員拍咗段片支持我地無人睇","createTime":"2019-10-13T16:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:24:55.000Z","uid":269125,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b2c78bfebbf16a03df64b19b2964afc373c7b4","tid":1652390,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q5HSVi3lDks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ5HSVi3lDks&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=4bc46d85\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q5HSVi3lDks</a><br />\n<br />\n又係我，上次攬炒巴搵英國議員段片又無人睇<br />\n今次比利時既港人組織拍既片都係無人睇<br />\n但問題唔係大家唔睇，而係拍片者同睇咗既人都唔幫手宣傳<br />\n唉，只好由我呢個Ｐ牌仔嚟<br />\n<br />\n先1:35，睇完俾個like，然後post上twitter多謝下人地<br />\n唔會浪費大家好多時間<br />\n<br />\n幫推唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4cc39f8375911f0c87c66c7aaf7d58a201451c","tid":1652390,"uid":44583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f4098c4d02e58550c850a53382757444aa608f84","tid":1652390,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"Help push"},{"pid":"13d9006a36474bdc401599429cc6ce846d80d794","tid":1652390,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680642dc1fb9c9f421ac754b785351b02cccaab3","tid":1652390,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e08751e602cd7ad7d91830e91013ae0836901338","tid":1652390,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/